# Math

#### Inline
Let $ F(u) $ be the *Fourier Transform* of the function $ f(x) $.

#### Block
$ F(u) = \int^{+\infty}_{-\infty} f(x) e^{-i 2\pi x} dx $

#### Multiline block

$$$
f(x) = \begin{cases} 
  x^2, & \text{if } x \ge 0 \\
  -x, & \text{if } x < 0
\end{cases}
$$$

